# CommonsBase_GNU

## Overview

GNU userland build tools (awk, bison, grep, make, GMP, Nettle, TLS …) packaged reproducibly for dk.

`CommonsBase_GNU` provides the GNU command-line tools that other dk packages
and your projects depend on, built once and content-addressed so every
platform gets a byte-identical, checksummed result.

## License

GPL-3.0-or-later

